=== Symbol Table Parsing โ `parse_symbol_table` function

$
parse\_symbols: IO \times SectionHeader \times StringTable \to List(SymbolEntry)
$

_Complexity constraint_:
$
|result| = \frac{section.size}{24} \quad \text{(symbol entry size)}
$

_Set-theoretic operation_:
$
\text{Filter: } \{s \in sections : s.type = SHT\_SYMTAB\}
\text{Map: } \{parse\_entry(s) : s \in symbol\_sections\}
$

_Direct code correspondence_:
```julia
= Mathematical model: parse_symbols: IO ร SectionHeader ร StringTable โ List(SymbolEntry)
function parse_symbol_table(io::IO, section::SectionHeader, strings::StringTable)::Vector{SymbolEntry}
    # Implementation of: symbol_count = section.size รท 24
    symbol_count = div(section.size, 24)     # โ size calculation
    symbols = Vector{SymbolEntry}()          # โ result collection
    for i in 1:symbol_count                  # โ bounded iteration
        entry = parse_symbol_entry(io)       # โ entry parsing
        entry.name = resolve_string(strings, entry.name_index)  # โ name resolution
        push!(symbols, entry)                # โ accumulation
    end
    return symbols
end
```

